                    own countrymen<hi xmlns:tei="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" rend="bold">.</hi>
                    <hi xmlns:tei="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" rend="bold">There are hardly five
                    critics in America, and several of them are asleep.</hi>
                    <hi xmlns:tei="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" rend="bold">A</hi>s for<lb/>
                    patronage<hi xmlns:tei="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" rend="bold">,</hi> it is
